## Ashby autofill helper

This repo now includes `autofill_ashby.py`, a Playwright script that automatically fills the Whatnot application form using `profile.json`.

### Run

```bash
python3 -m pip install playwright
python3 -m playwright install chromium
python3 autofill_ashby.py
```

The script fills all supported fields automatically, pauses for manual review, and leaves final submission to you (including CAPTCHA).
